Class SimpleListTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • cse360assign2.SimpleListTest
  • public class SimpleListTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class: SimpleListTest
    The SimpleListTest class contains 36 test cases (18 success, 18 fail). It has a private SimpleList object. The test object is used in every test to provide a basic simple list for modification. It tests all 6 methods including the base constructor SimpleList(), add(int),remove(int), int count(), String toString(), and int search().
